# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AGRIMODEL PRO — ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# Copy this to .env in your project root before deploying
# In Netlify/Vercel: add these in the dashboard under
#   Site Settings → Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── ANTHROPIC (required for AI report generation) ─────────────
# Get this from console.anthropic.com → API Keys
VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here

# ── PAYFAST (required for live payments) ──────────────────────
# Get these from payfast.io → Dashboard → Integration
VITE_PF_MERCHANT_ID=your-merchant-id
VITE_PF_MERCHANT_KEY=your-merchant-key
VITE_PF_PASSPHRASE=your-passphrase

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DEPLOYMENT CHECKLIST
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# 1. INSTALL & BUILD
#    npm install
#    npm run build
#    → produces /dist folder
#
# 2. NETLIFY (recommended — free tier works)
#    a. netlify.com → New site → Import from Git (or drag /dist)
#    b. Build command:  npm run build
#       Publish dir:    dist
#    c. Add env vars above in Site Settings → Environment Variables
#    d. Deploy
#
# 3. VERCEL (alternative)
#    a. vercel.com → New Project → Import Git repo
#    b. Framework: Vite
#    c. Add env vars in Settings → Environment Variables
#    d. Deploy
#
# 4. PAYFAST GO-LIVE CHECKLIST
#    a. Sign up at payfast.io → Business account
#    b. Verify bank account (2-3 business days)
#    c. Get Merchant ID + Merchant Key from dashboard
#    d. Set passphrase in payfast.io → Settings → Security
#    e. Add all 3 credentials to env vars above
#    f. In src/App.jsx find: sandbox: true
#       Change to:           sandbox: false
#    g. Rebuild & redeploy
#
# 5. PAYFAST ITN (payment notification — important for production)
#    When a payment completes, PayFast POSTs to your notifyUrl.
#    For Netlify: add a serverless function at
#    netlify/functions/payfast-notify.js
#    For Vercel: add api/payfast-notify.js
#    Minimum implementation: verify signature, record payment, return 200
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PRICING
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Report price: R1,500 (set in src/App.jsx → PF.price)
# PayFast fee:  3.5% + R2.00 = ~R54.50 per transaction
# Net per sale: ~R1,445.50
# Anthropic API cost per report: ~R1.20 (claude-sonnet, ~8k tokens)
# Net margin per report: ~R1,444
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
